<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Trading Terminal | Ghost Print AI</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Grotesk:wght@300;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body { 
            background-color: #050505; 
            background-image: radial-gradient(#10b98110 1px, transparent 1px);
            background-size: 30px 30px;
            color: #fafafa; 
            font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif; 
        }
        .glass-card {
            background: rgba(15, 15, 15, 0.7);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.2);
        }
        .download-btn {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #10b981 0%, #059669 100%);
            transition: 0.3s;
        }
        .download-btn:hover { transform: scale(1.02); box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.4); }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="p-6 md:p-12">

    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <header class="flex justify-between items-center mb-12">
            <h1 class="text-xl font-bold text-emerald-500 tracking-tighter">GHOST TERMINAL</h1>
            <span class="text-[10px] text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-widest">Authorized Access Only</span>
        </header>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
            <div class="glass-card p-8 rounded-2xl">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">SMC Precision Indicator</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mb-6">Version 4.0 (MT4/MT5 Compatible). Includes Precision Gap Algorithm logic.</p>
                <a href="YOUR_LINK_TO_INDICATOR_FILE" class="download-btn block text-center py-4 rounded-xl font-bold uppercase text-xs tracking-widest">Download File</a>
            </div>

            <div class="glass-card p-8 rounded-2xl">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Ghost Print Bot</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mb-6">Execution engine for Synthetic Indices. Optimized for high concurrency.</p>
                <a href="YOUR_LINK_TO_BOT_FILE" class="download-btn block text-center py-4 rounded-xl font-bold uppercase text-xs tracking-widest">Download Bot</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-12 p-6 border border-emerald-900/30 rounded-xl bg-emerald-950/10 text-center">
            <p class="text-xs text-emerald-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Need License Key?</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">If your tool asks for a key, contact <a href="https://t.me/AdamsFX_Support" class="underline text-white">Adams Support</a> with your M-Pesa ID.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
      
